</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-5d">From question, we can see that motion (including rotation) takes place in xy-plane. It, then, follows that angular velocity is perpendicular to xy-plane i.e. it is directed along z-axis. Let angular velocity be represented as :
</para>
