</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
 </para>
<para id="element-98g">where “<term>r</term>” determines the position of the particle with respect to the point. The magnitude of angular velocity can be determined, using any of the following two relations :
 </para>
<para id="element-98h"><m:math display="block">
